Below are a number of tricks to help reduce unwanted answers

 1) Tell the engine to not "Guess"
     . I am going to ask a series of question that are related to xxxxxx. If you can't prove your answer with a yyyyyyyy URL then say, "I can't prove this answer". Follow up your thoughts on what you think it could be.

 2) Ask the engine to "Bold" all changes in any follow up questions

